profile:
At Consumer Choice Roofing and Drainage we have been proudly providing our Roofing Services to The Greater Vancouver Area and the Greater Fraser Valley. Learn more about why Consumer Choice Roofing and Drainage is a great choice for your roofing, drainage, chimney repairs, brick work and concrete in Vancouver, Lower Mainland and the Greater Fraser Valley.
 
We work hard to be the consumer choice for, new construction roofing, residential roofing, commercial roofing, multi-family roofing and for emergency roof repairs in British Columbia. We have offices in Richmond and Vancouver to help service our customers in the lower mainland. Over the many years we have earned a reputation for integrity, quality and honesty. 
 
Buildings require the right people for installation and maintenance tasks. We provide various residential and commercial contractor services in and around Vancouver. Our customers keep coming back because we offer them services that meet, if not exceed, their needs.
 
Services: Roofing, drainage, Chimney Repairs, Brickwork, Flashing, Tuckpointing, Rebuilding, Aluminum & Stainless Chimney liners, All Chimney Repairs, Planter Repairs,  Waterproofing, Sidewalks (Broom Finish, Exposed aggregate, stamped Concrete), Driveways (Broom Finish, Exposed aggregate, stamped Concrete), Foundation Repairs, Removal & Replacement have you covered. Single car garage to residential homes, commercial builders or industrial complex's Consumers Choice Roofing & Drainage.
